![Burning150.jpg](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1603886865355-HXT6MYYQ3UIR81T8VCSD/Burning150.jpg)

**EPISODE 150 is upon us...**but so is Halloween! In order to celebrate both, we are going to discuss everyone's favorite working class warlock, the cynical sorcerer and manipulative magician John Constantine! Not only has Constantine managed to keep himself relevant for the last 35 years but his popularity was at its peak in 2005 when he was given his own feature film. In this HISTORICAL episode we tackle the movie, the tale its based on (Dangerous Habits by Garth Ennis) and debate the similarities and differences! Join us as we get manically morbid on our 150th Episode!  
**  
